{{/*
Purpose: Per-turn skill routing guide shown to the model as a numbered list.
Used by: intent.FormatSkillCatalog → runtime.skillCatalogMessage (system message each turn).
Data: prompt.SkillCatalogData, prompt.SkillRow
*/}}
## {{.Title}}

Before calling any skill-scoped tool, you MUST call {{.ActivateSkillTool}} with the matching skill name.

{{- range $i, $skill := .Skills}}
{{add $i 1}}. **{{$skill.Name}}** — {{$skill.Description}}
{{- if $skill.Triggers}}
   - Use when: {{join $skill.Triggers ", "}}
{{- end}}
{{- range $skill.Examples}}
   - Example: {{printf "%q" .}}
{{- end}}
   - Activate: {{$.ActivateSkillTool}}({"name":"{{$skill.Name}}"})
{{- end}}
